#: ../../architecture.rst:80
msgid ""
"``ServiceProxy`` 只保存可序列化的句柄和配置，不保存锁、连接池或后台线程。Ray Task 因此只需要接收 一个服务容器；环境 "
"router、trace 与 replay 由 driver 或 CLI 统一创建，LLM client 只携带连接参数， worker "
"在自己的事件循环中按需创建 litellm Router 和并发控制器。"
msgstr ""
"``ServiceProxy`` stores only serializable handles and configuration. It does not store "
"locks, connection pools, or background threads. A Ray Task therefore only needs to "
"receive one service container. The environment router, trace, and replay are created "
"once by the driver or CLI; the LLM client only carries connection parameters, and "
"workers create the litellm Router and concurrency controller on demand in their own "
"event loop."

#: ../../architecture.rst:85
msgid "环境路由"
msgstr "Environment Routing"

#: ../../architecture.rst:87
msgid ""
"环境状态由环境路由统一管理。生产运行时，CLI 会通过 ``get_env_router_actor_class`` 创建专用的 Ray "
"actor，并把 ``EnvRouterProxy`` 放入 ``ServiceProxy``。智能体通过该 proxy 调用 ``ask``、 "
"``step``、``init`` 和 ``get_world_description`` 等接口；所有智能体看到的是同一份环境状态。"
msgstr ""
"Environment state is managed by the environment router. In production "
"runtime, the CLI creates a dedicated Ray actor through "
"``get_env_router_actor_class`` and places an ``EnvRouterProxy`` in "
"``ServiceProxy``. Agents call ``ask``, ``step``, ``init``, "
"``get_world_description``, and related interfaces through that proxy; all"
" agents see the same environment state.\n"

