msgstr ":mod:`agentsociety2.trace` provides distributed tracing:"

#: ../../architecture.rst:155
msgid "``ShardedTraceWriter`` 按 ``trace_id`` 分片写入，并通过后台线程批量落盘。"
msgstr ""
"``ShardedTraceWriter`` shards writes by ``trace_id`` and flushes them in "
"batches through a background thread.\n"

#: ../../architecture.rst:156
msgid ""
"``JsonlTraceWriter`` 提供 "
"``start_span``、``trace_span``、``record_event``、``end_span`` 和 "
"``TraceSpan``。"
msgstr ""
